有趣的是，&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!--
- effectivness
  - 不只是 pipeline 本身的效率，而是要連下游一併考慮
    - 為了讀取做最佳化
  - latency
  - 第二條 pipeline
  - pre-aggregate

- extensibility
- complexity

- scalability

- maintainability
  - bug reproduce
  - disaster recovery

- reliability
  - sla
  - monitor
    - corruptted input

- usability
  - easy to use / understand

